### 0h Game Jam

[0h Game Jam](0hgame) is a coding competition that takes place during
[DST hour shift](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daylight_saving_time).

* ### Huh
	Click on a free spot to survive. Made for [0h Game Jam][0hgame] 2014.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in October 2014</span>$(loc ../huh:submission)</p>

	+ [Play](http://hhsw.de/sites/proto/huh/)
	+ [Timelapse](https://vimeo.com/110055282)

## Old games
* ### Striker
	Very fast vertical shooter. Doesn't work well on mobile.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in April 2012</span>$(loc ../Striker js/src src)</p>

	+ [Play](http://striker.markusfisch.de/)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/Striker)
* ### Sheeptris
	Multiplayer Tetris with Sheeps. Requires
	[Java in the browser](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_applet).
	Doesn't work on mobile.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in July 2004</span>$(loc ../Sheeptris)</p>

	+ [Play](http://hhsw.de/sites/sheeptris/)

## Tutorial

* ### How to make a web game from scratch
	A talk I held in 2015 at [FrankenJS](http://www.frankenjs.org/) about
	making simple games from scratch using vanilla JavaScript.

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/web-game-from-scratch-talk)

